snippet.title: "I Want Emilia Clarke" Jason Momoa Speaks On Who Should Play Mera In Aquaman 2
snippet.description:
"I Want Emilia Clarke" Jason Momoa Speaks On Who Should Play Mera In Aquaman 2 
The legal battle between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp has gone on for so many years, affecting all aspects of their lives, and now, it has started affecting their careers. Johnny Depp has lost most of his major roles such as Jack Sparrow in Pirates of the Caribbean and Grindelwald in Fantastic Beasts. Amber has also not been left unscathed by the situation since she is now about to lose her biggest role so far which is Mera in Aquaman. Now, Jason Momoa wants Emilia Clarke to Replace her.


Here on Film Streak we are all about the latest spill in Hollywood! You can rest assure that we will bring you all the latest celebrity drama and gossip especially concerning you favorite actors!
